  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0bc2\u0bb0\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0b95\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd - \u0b87\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0bb3\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Armed forces may act to escalate violence - Army Spokesman",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "During the demonstration in the Parliament premises on Wednesday, the security forces were seriously attacked by two demonstrators and their T-56 rifle was fired at them.",
        "Military spokesperson Brigadier Nilantha Premaratne said that the general public should act with awareness as those who have seized the gun may use it to increase violence.",
        "Brigadier Nilantha Premaratne, who issued a special announcement in this regard today, further mentioned,",
        "Efforts have been made to create clashes with the security forces by the parties who acted violently in Bhattaramulla - Parliament area and nearby areas on Wednesday.",
        "Two of the security forces who went forward to control it were severely and inhumanely assaulted on the face and head with iron rods and polas.",
        "After carrying out the attacks, they looted two T-56 rifles and the ammunition used for them.",
        "Thus, the security personnel who were badly hit on the face and head are being treated in the hospital in a critical condition.",
        "With the guns seized from them, the parties may act to spread violence further. Therefore, we request the general public to act with awareness in this regard, he said."
      ],
